@finiasz I made changes to revert #3293 from 2.13, so things should work in 2.13.3.

I pushed `2.13.3-SNAPSHOT` to Sonatype snapshot repository so if there's any chance you could verify functioning, that'd be great -- there are quite a few places where `getParameterCount()` is called, but not all of them are related to `Method`.
But I hope I did not miss something.
